007 was repealed and subsec. (g) redesignated (f) by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/264/tIX/s904/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–264, title IX, § 904(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-10-09"},"text":"Oct. 9, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3276"},"text":"110 Stat. 3276","children":[],"tail":". Section 6007 was subsequently repealed and reenacted as "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s49106"},"text":"section 49106 of Title 49","children":[],"tail":", Transportation, by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/102"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–102","children":[],"tail":", §§ 2(26), 5(b), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-11-20"},"text":"Nov. 20, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/2205"},"text":"111 Stat. 2205","children":[],"tail":", 2217, and does not contain provisions relating to a Board of Review."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idcc70752f-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2024—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/63"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–63","children":[],"tail":" struck out par. (2) designation before “Any action” and struck out par. (1) which read as follows: “If any provision of the Metropolitan Washington Airports Amendments Act of 1996 (title IX of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/264"},"text":"Public Law 104–264","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3274"},"text":"110 Stat. 3274","children":[],"tail":") or the amendments made by the Act, or the application of that provision to a person, circumstance, or venue, is held invalid by a judicial order, the Secretary of Transportation and the Metropolitan Washington Airports Authority shall be subject to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s49108"},"text":"section 49108 of this title","children":[],"tail":" from the day after the day the order is issued.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
